T02D3312:11a-1: a'arya manydzu shr'i s'a dha nam /
T02D3312:11a-5: rnam dag 'jam dpal sgrub pa'i thabs //
T02D3312:11a-6: shin tu gsal zhing mdor bsdus pa //
T02D3312:11a-7: mi shes rab rib 'joms par byed //
T02D3312:11a-8: dam pa rnams phyir legs brjod bya //
T02D3312:11a-9: stong pa nyid kyi rjes su de bzhin du snying
T02D3312:11a-10: gar yi ge mu:ser po yongs su gyur pa las
T02D3312:11a-11: / 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa zhal gsum phyag
T02D3312:11b-0: drug @11b pa gur gum dmar po 'dra zhing sngon
T02D3312:11b-1: / po dang / dkar po ni g-yas dang cig shos kyi zhal lo //
T02D3312:11b-2: sems dpa'i skyil mo krung dang ldan pa /
T02D3312:11b-3: ral gri dang mda' dang mchog sbyin pa ni g-yas kyi phyag gsum na'o //
T02D3312:11b-4: shes rab kyi pha rol tu phyin pa'i glegs bam dang /
T02D3312:11b-6: gzhu ni g-yon ba'i phyag gsum na'o //
T02D3312:11b-7: sgeg pa dang bcas shing gzhon nu'i rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
T02D3312:11b-8: kha dog sna tshogs kyi gos dang /
T02D3312:11b-9: me tog la sogs pas brgyan par byas shing lcang lo gsum gyis mdzes pa'o //
T02D3312:11b-10: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rdul phra rab las yongs su rdzogs pa'i bdag nyid bsgom bar bya'o //
T02D3312:11b-11: aom mu:zhes bya ba'i sngags bzlas par bya'o //
T02D3312:11b-12: 'phags pa 'jam dpal gyi sgrub thabs rdzogs so //
